{"tid":113154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"群組稱浙江足浴店火警不止18死　女子涉虛構擾秩序被拘留10日　","createTime":"2017-02-08T16:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T17:04:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d000881299f031e3645b2099b37c656dd75a2fc","tid":113154,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"2017年2月8日 星期三 <br />\n下一篇<br />\n微信群組稱浙江足浴店火警不止18死　女子涉虛構擾秩序被拘留10日　網民嘲發言與官方不一都是謠言<br />\n<br />\n浙江天台縣一間足浴店本月5日發生火警，造成18死。天台縣警方表示，今日拘捕一名女子，指其在微信群組發布虛假消息，需被行政拘留10天。<br />\n《新京報》報道，一名裘姓女子在足浴店發生火災後兩日，在一個有500人的微信群組中發布意外死亡人數<span style=\"color: red;\">「肯定不止18個」、「據說玉湖拆房子也死了好多人」等信息</span>。天台縣公安局消息指裘女未經核實擅自發布虛假信息，在社會上造成惡劣影響，已將她拘捕，而裘女到案後，亦對自己的行為供認不諱。公安局表示，裘涉虛構事實擾亂公共秩序，被處以行政拘留10日的處罰。<br />\n有關報道吸引不少網民留言討論，<span style=\"color: red;\">「官僚所說的每一句話，百姓都在質疑！百姓質疑的每一件事，官僚都在否認！官僚否認的每一件事，最後都被證實！」</span>、「抓得挺快。穿山甲慘死這麼久了，還不知道兇手是誰」、「懷疑就拘留?」、「只要和官方發言不一樣，都是謠言！」、「寧夏石嘴山市交警嚴重違法違紀，老百姓反映了一年為什麼沒人查？」、「動作真快，穩」、「警察只有幹這個是神速」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170208/s00004/1486543624605SL4_C2C2A06A1454C8CD470C7D9BD5E2C0FF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170208%2Fs00004%2F1486543624605SL4_C2C2A06A1454C8CD470C7D9BD5E2C0FF.jpg&h=834eb20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170208/s00004/1486542666280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170208%2Fs00004%2F1486542666280&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a7922871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170208%2Fs00004%2F1486542666280&h=e240995d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170208/s00004/1486542666280</a>"},{"pid":"43f06e68a618b15f8e6edb26ecba99d53e2543b6","tid":113154,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8eb2f38d6cd139a80a513e3578664fe72759269","tid":113154,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:29:30.000Z","msg":"殊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287f0c4e34376f35cca947cc96573cdee12ada2e","tid":113154,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T20:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e3dc9f3462038097baa105463cc3822ff92e421","tid":113154,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T20:06:32.000Z","msg":"不誠實使用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f6bb404bcd6c260fe52ad88a0cdf4b23274a35","tid":113154,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">This </span></span>"},{"pid":"b8c3c4d60e5a27326b0ecab56f89bf0936d3f5cf","tid":113154,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"你知道得太多了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a070cf99d9c46d21b81d2dd83e676ecc1e792c0a","tid":113154,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"捉得咁即係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a58d3d91f53c0c081d2fcc17a38f7ccf2f6f25","tid":113154,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉得咁即係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa37e4974d39a6a86b9d45bac8